description: BoMill AB develops, manufactures and sells grain sorting technology. The firm offers quality sorting technology for wheat, durum wheat, barley and oats. Solutions include detection of fusarium infected kernels, detection of non-vitreous kernels, separation of the strongest kernels in a batch, prediction of protein content of individual kernels, among others. The Company’s primary distribution markets are Europe, North America and Australia.
